title: How to Self-Publish Your E-Book
description: If you have a story you want to share, you can easily publish your work in popular electronic bookstores — and maybe even make a little money.

title: Tired of Dating Apps, Some Turn to Google Docs
description: Writers of so-called Date-Me Docs, which can read like 1,000-word versions of the personal ads of yore, hope for a more meaningful connection than a swipe might allow.
